Message,Bus,is,a,messaging,service,that,allows,developers,to,add,messaging,capabilities,to,their,websites,and,applications,Through,the,Message,Bus,API,developers,can,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,the,Message,Bus,Global,Delivery,Network,with,other,applications,and,websites,Public,documentation,is,not,available,interested,developers,should,sign,up,here,for,more,information,https,www,messagebus,com,features,api,smtp